º Why Q-Setup? ³
ÈÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍ¾

    This program is useless for those who doesn't use the  wonderful viewer
QView by Alexandr Gazko. This program will help you to easily configure the
viewer as you prefer and will show you all changes you made on-fly. See the
QVIEW.DOC for more details about the settings.

