º Mouse support ³
ÈÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍ¾

    The program should work correctly with any type of mouse.  There is  no
difference between the rigth & middle (if any) mouse buttons.
    The left mouse button is  similar to <Enter> key, but if pressed in the
bottom line of screen it calls Help.
    The right button is always similar to <Alt-F5> combination.
    In tables use double-click to accept.

